C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETaylor%20Rains%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20offer%20some%20last-minute%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20looks%20like%20Mother%20Nature%20might%20cause%20some%20issues%20this%20year.%20Portions%20of%20the%20Midwest%2C%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20East%20Coast%20are%20expecting%20inclement%20weather%20today.%20How%20bad%20could%20that%20make%20things%20not%20just%20for%20those%20areas%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaylor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThunderstorms%20around%20Dallas%2FFort%20Worth%20already%20caused%20hundreds%20of%20delays%20at%20the%20city's%20two%20main%20airports%20on%20Monday.%20And%20these%20local%20disruptions%20can%20ripple%20through%20an%20airline's%20entire%20network%2C%20displacing%20aircraft%2C%20pilots%2C%20and%20flight%20attendants%20(the%20crew%20can%20%26quot%3Btime%20out%26quot%3B%20after%20prolonged%20delays%20and%20become%20legally%20unable%20to%20fly).%20So%20even%20if%20it's%20sunny%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20your%20flight%20could%20be%20three%20hours%20late%20due%20to%20thunderstorms%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gets%20even%20trickier%20if%20you're%20flying%20out%20of%20a%20smaller%20airport%2C%20like%20Key%20West%20or%20White%20Plains%2C%20where%20it's%20harder%20for%20airlines%20to%20quickly%20find%20replacement%20aircraft%20or%20crew%20when%20things%20get%20out%20of%20sync%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20they%20can't%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYikes!%20So%20if%20you%20find%20yourself%20facing%20serious%20delays%2C%20what's%20the%20best%20thing%20a%20beleaguered%20traveler%20can%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaylor%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20First%2C%20don't%20panic%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20options.%20During%20a%20delay%20or%20cancellation%2C%20the%20fastest%20route%20is%20usually%20your%20airline's%20app%20or%20website%2C%20where%20you%20can%20rebook%20online%20on%20an%20earlier%20flight%2C%20a%20later%20one%2C%20or%20even%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20is%20typically%20quicker%20than%20waiting%20in%20long%20airport%20lines%20or%20clogged%20phone%20queues.%20You%20can%20also%20try%20combining%20both%3A%20wait%20in%20line%20while%20simultaneously%20rebooking%20online%20to%20boost%20your%20chances%20of%20resolving%20things%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGot%20it.%20Let's%20ratchet%20things%20up%20and%20say%20no%20rebooking%20options%20exist.%20Then%20what%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaylor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20depends%20on%20who's%20at%20fault.%20For%20overnight%20delays%20caused%20by%20the%20airline%2C%20such%20as%20maintenance%20or%20crew%20staffing%20issues%2C%20most%20carriers%20will%20provide%20complimentary%20accommodations%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20meals.%20You%20can%20verify%20policies%20through%20the%20government's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transportation.gov%2Fairconsumer%2Fairline-cancellation-delay-dashboard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAirline%20Customer%20Service%20Dashboard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20disruption%20is%20beyond%20the%20airline's%20control%2C%20such%20as%20weather%2C%20compensation%20is%20less%20guaranteed.%20Some%20airlines%20may%20offer%20meal%20vouchers%20as%20a%20goodwill%20gesture%2C%20but%20they%20aren't%20required%20to.%20Still%2C%20it's%20worth%20asking.%20You%20may%20also%20be%20able%20to%20recoup%20costs%20through%20travel%20insurance%20built%20into%20the%20credit%20card%20you%20used%20to%20book%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20card%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20reimbursed%20me%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20remember%3A%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20full%20refund%20for%20any%20canceled%20flight%2C%20regardless%20of%20reason%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20rebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOk%2C%20I%20saved%20the%20most%20important%20question%20for%20last%3A%20Window%20or%20aisle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaylor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20used%20to%20be%20a%20window%20seat%20fan%2C%20but%20I'll%20always%20pay%20up%20for%20an%20aisle%20now!%20I%20didn't%20stop%20flying%20when%20I%20was%20pregnant%2C%20so%20I%20think%20having%20easy%20access%20to%20the%20bathroom%20or%20to%20stretch%20converted%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-what-to-do-thanksgiving-travel-chaos-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764156443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6926104eabd5e944effb7e26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-what-to-do-thanksgiving-travel-chaos-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20to%20do%20if%20your%20flight%20gets%20delayed%20or%20canceled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco%2CTaylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-what-to-do-thanksgiving-travel-chaos-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20fire%20engulfs%20multiple%20high%20rises%20in%20Hong%20Kong%3B%20at%20least%204%20dead%20-%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764156228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-125588344%2Cimgsize-1120143.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fmassive-fire-engulfs-multiple-high-rises-in-hong-kong-at-least-4-dead-video%2Farticleshow%2F125588308.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20devastating%20fire%20ripped%20through%20multiple%20high-rise%20towers%20at%20Wang%20Fuk%20Court%20in%20Hong%20Kong's%20Tai%20Po%20district%2C%20claiming%20at%20least%20four%20lives%20and%20trapping%20several%20o