3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20it's%20like%20at%20the%20iconic%20bell-ringing%20that%20kicks%20off%20a%20day%20of%20trading.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ffirst-trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20markets%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we're%20talking%20famous%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20three%20that%20come%20to%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20the%20Pope's%20at%20the%20Vatican%2C%20from%20where%20he%20blesses%20Saint%20Peter's%20Square.%20Then%20there's%20Juliet's%20balcony%20in%20Verona%2C%20Italy%2C%20from%20Shakespeare's%20%26quot%3BRomeo%20and%20Juliet.%26quot%3B%20And%20for%20us%20market%20geeks%2C%20you%20have%20the%20holy%20grail%3A%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange's%20iconic%20bell-ringing%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20opening%20and%20close%20of%20every%20trading%20session%20at%20the%20NYSE%2C%20VIPs%20head%20up%20to%20the%20atrium%20gallery%20and%20ring%20a%20brass%20bell%2C%20as%20if%20to%20profess%20their%20love%20for%2C%20or%20say%20their%20prayers%20to%2C%20public%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NYSE%20has%20used%20a%20bell%20to%20open%20and%20close%20the%20market%20since%201903%2C%20when%20it%20first%20relocated%20to%20its%2011%20Wall%20Street%20location%2C%20making%20it%20a%20long-standing%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20important%20symbol%20for%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Taylor%2C%20NYSE's%20chief%20development%20officer%20and%20head%20of%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20I%20visited%20the%20exchange%20to%20see%20the%20bell%20ringing%20up%20close.%20Here's%20what%20the%20experience%20was%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDelta's%20CEO%20was%20ringing%20the%20bell%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20delta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C