0width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c659e1a9cbb014deeac9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20the%20morning%20in%20a%20boardroom%2C%20where%20they're%20served%20breakfast%2C%20guests%20then%20head%20upstairs%20to%20the%20trading%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFamiliar%20faces%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c6bd89026fbb4d0e5adb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20market%20hadn't%20opened%20yet%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20pretty%20quiet.%20Looking%20around%20at%20the%20trading%20posts%2C%20I%20recognized%20many%20of%20the%20faces%20I've%20seen%20in%20photos%20from%20the%20trading%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHi%2C%20Jim%20and%20Carl%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c702e1a9cbb014deead9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2020%20minutes%20before%20the%20bell%20rang%2C%20I%20headed%20up%20toward%20the%20bell-ringing%20area%20and%20caught%20an%20up-close%20look%20at%20CNBC%20hosts%20Jim%20Cramer%20and%20Carl%20Quintanilla.%20The%20set%20is%20positioned%20at%20what%20used%20to%20be%20trading%20post%20nine%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20the%20bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESigning%20the%20guest%20book%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c726e1a9cbb014deeae3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20about%209%3A20%2C%20Bastian%20and%20the%20other%20Delta%20guests%20came%20up%20to%20sign%20the%20NYSE's%20guest%20book.%20NYSE%20President%20Lynn%20Martin%20joined%20them.%20The%20exchange%20has%20stacks%20of%20guest%20books%20going%20back%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESet%20for%20the%20opening%20bell%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c8c9e1a9cbb014deeb28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20the%20LED%20screen%20behind%20the%20bell%20balcony%20opened%20up%2C%20and%20Martin%20and%20Bastian%20appeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20Martin%20or%20Taylor%20usually%20accompanies%20the%20guests%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%20giving%20them%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20a%20clock%20across%20from%20the%20balcony%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c7f0abd5e944effb7069%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20from%20the%20balcony%2C%20there's%20a%20clock%20and%20TV%20screen%20showing%20the%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20open%2C%20the%20bell%20rings%2010%20seconds%20before%209%3A30%20am%2C%20and%20the%20trading%20session%20begins%20when%20the%20ringing%20ends.%20At%20the%20close%2C%20the%20bell%20starts%20ringing%20at%203%3A59%3A45%2C%20letting%20traders%20know%20they%20have%2015%20seconds%20to%20get%20their%20last%20trades%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20thirty%20seconds%20before%20the%20bell%20rings%2C%20the%20NYSE%20staff%20pumps%20up%20the%20bell%20ringers%20and%20the%20onlookers%2C%20rousing%20applause%20and%20cheers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuests%20actually%20ring%20the%20bell%20by%20pushing%20a%20button.%20Sometimes%2C%20Taylor%20said%2C%20things%20can%20go%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20for%20the%20bell%20ringer%20to%20understand%20that%20they're%20actually%20controlling%20the%20bell%20and%20there's%20a%20purpose%20for%20it.%20Because%20if%20they%20screw%20up%2C%20the%20traders%20will%20derisively%20boo%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20start%20clapping%2030%20seconds%20before%2C%20and%20I%20always%20warn%20people%2C%20'When%20I%20say%20here%20we%20go%2C%20that%20is%20not%20for%20the%20bell%2C%20that's%20for%20clapping.'%20Every%20once%20in%20a%20while%20someone%20will%20start%20ringing%20the%20bell%20way%20too%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20went%20smoothly%20this%20time%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%20opening%20bell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c92c89026fbb4d0e5b42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKudos%20to%20Bastian%2C%20who%20rang%20the%20bell%20punctually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nyse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6925c7c5abd5e944effb7065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20bell%2C%20the%20folks%20at%20NYSE%20were%20nice%20enough%20to%20take%20me%20backstage%2C%20along%20the%20route%20that%20bell-r