strike-group-to-caribbean-drug-war-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrug%20traffickers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20will%20change%20up%20tactics%20based%20on%20what's%20been%20observed%20from%20recent%20real-world%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20piloting%20of%20the%20Dolphin%20is%20something%20that's%20%26quot%3Bpredictable%20and%20intuitive%20to%20you%20when%20you've%20been%20training%20for%20thousands%20of%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Choker%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20training%20in%20order%20to%20know%20that%20I%20need%20the%20helicopter%20to%20do%20an%20extreme%20angle%20of%20bank%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20only%20move%20my%20hand%20three-fourths%20of%20an%20inch%20in%20order%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrecision%20marksmen%20are%20likewise%20constantly%20training%20to%20get%20the%20perfect%20shot%20while%20maintaining%20clear%20communication%20with%20the%20pilots.%20The%20training%20pipeline%20requires%20knowledge%20of%20what%20weapons%20to%20use%20for%20specific%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Coast%20Guard%20crew%20members%20stand%20on%20a%20ship%20behind%20three%20Yahama%20boat%20engines%20and%20in%20front%20of%20an%20orange%20helicopter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69252e1289026fbb4d0e5664%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETK%3Cp%3EUS%20Coast%20Guard%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mounted%20machine%20gun%20on%20the%20Dolphin%20is%20for%20firing%20warning%20shots%20when%20a%20suspected%20drug%20vessel%20doesn't%20stop%20after%20initial%20verbal%20warnings.%20Other%20rifles%2C%20like%20the%20M107%20semi-automatic%20.50%20caliber%20sniper%20rifle%20and%20M110%20Semi%20Automatic%20Sniper%20System%20chambered%20for%207.62%C3%9751mm%20NATO-standard%20rounds%2C%20are%20useful%20for%20knocking%20out%20vessel%20engines%20depending%20on%20t