%20of%20%26quot%3Byour%20girlfriend%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20indeed%20a%20major%20decision%20that%20will%20impact%20both%20of%20you%20greatly%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20essential%20that%20you%20reach%20a%20final%2C%20mutually%20agreed-upon%20decision%20as%20a%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20be%20part%20of%20that%20decision%2C%20you%20have%20to%20know%20what%20%3Cem%3Eyou%3C%2Fem%3E%20want%20first%3B%20otherwise%2C%20it's%20not%20your%20decision%20at%20all%2C%20is%20it%3F%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20we%20go%20around%20and%20around%20issues%20inside%20our%20heads%2C%20our%20true%20opinions%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20internal%20noise.%20Processing%20your%20situation%20aloud%20with%20a%20friend%20will%20allow%20you%20the%20space%20to%20hear%20your%20thoughts%20and%20feelings.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you%20listen%20to%20yourself%20with%20curiosity%20and%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20suggest%20bringing%20your%20parents%20into%20this%20decision-making%20process%20at%20all.%20Your%20life%20with%20your%20girlfriend%20is%20shared%20between%20the%20two%20of%20you.%20Your%20actual%20lived%20experiences%20immediately%20outrank%20any%20notions%20your%20parents%20have%20about%20propriety%20and%20morality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-help-financially-call-it-loan-against-inheritance-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elife-changing%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20they're%20offering%20must%20feel%20tempting%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20it's%20a%20gift%2C%20not%20a%20prize.%20You%20can't%20earn%20it%2C%20nor%20should%20you%20try.%20Whether%20your%20parents%20choose%20to%20give%20you%20that%20gift%20is%20up%20to%20them.%20Any%20attempt%20on%20your%20part%20to%20persuade%20them%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20the%20down%20payment%20will%20only%20create%20a%20toxic%20cycle%20of%20mutual%20manipulation%2C%20where%20they%20treat%20the%20money%20like%20puppet%20strings%20while%20you%20treat