2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumane-ai-pin-shows-life-after-smartphones-remains-distant-fantasy-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euseful%20than%20your%20smartphone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20most%20useful%20thing%20you%20can%20have!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20boring%20scenario%2C%20which%20I%20fear%20sounds%20fairly%20likely%2C%20is%20that%20it's%20some%20sort%20of%20audio%20device%20that%20uses%20ChatGPT%2C%20like%20a%20small%20speaker%20you%20can%20talk%20to%20as%20an%20assistant%20that%20listens%20and%20learns.%20(OpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20my%20request%20for%20comment%20or%20for%20more%20information%20on%20the%20device.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20seen%20some%20examples%20of%20devices%20like%20this.%20The%20AI%20Pin%20was%20a%20small%20clip-on%20wearable%20that%20could%20see%20and%20hear%20the%20world%20around%20you%20to%20give%20you%20AI-powered%20information.%20(An%20interesting%20example%20was%20holding%20up%20a%20fruit%20to%20it%20in%20the%20grocery%20store%20and%20asking%20it%20how%20much%20sugar%20it%20contained.)%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumane-shutting-down-some-buyers-not-get-refund-ai-pins-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20Pin%20crashed%20and%20burned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plagued%20by%20bad%20reviews%20and%20buggy%20service.%20It%20was%2C%20perhaps%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20its%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20tested%20it%2C%20but%20I%20had%20a%20mixed%20reaction%20when%20it%20launched%3A%20I%20have%20enormous%20hesistations%20about%20the%20idea%20that%20voice%20control%20is%20the%20way%20of%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20would%20be%20far%20too%20embarassed%20to%20talk%20out%20loud%20to%20a%20device%20in%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20and%20I%20also%20know%20my%20coworkers%20would%20ring%20my%20neck%20if%20I%20were%20using%20it%20in%20our%20open%20office.%20And%20yet%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20still%20kind%20of%20wanted%20it.%20It%20looked%20cool!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-needs-friends-wearable-ai-friend-companion-review-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFriend%20necklace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20wearable%20that%20listened%20to%20your%20conversations%20and%20would%20chat%20to%20you%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend%26quot%3B%20(%3F%3F%3F)%20had%20an%20ignoble%20launch.%20The%20startup%20bought%20a%20massive%20ad%20campaign%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20subway%2C%20and%20its%20posters%20were%20immediately%20vandalized%20by%20those%20who%20found%20the%20concept%20of%20an%20AI%20friend%20dystopian%20(whether%20the%20backlash%20was%20encouraged%20as%20part%20of%20some%204D%20chess%20master%20marketing%20plan%2C%20that's%20something%20I%20simply%20don't%20care%20to%20put%20too%20many%20brain%20cells%20into%20considering).%20The%20Friend%20necklace%20also%20suffered%20from%20bad%20reviews%20about%20its%20buggy%20service%20and%20unappealing%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20more%20low-key%20and%20less%20ambitious%20AI%20audio%20devices%20that%20perform%20straightforward%20tasks.%20The%20Plaud%20Note%20is%20a%20slim%20device%20that%20listens%20to%20your%20meeting%20or%20school%20lecture%20and%20takes%20notes.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20task%20AI%20is%20great%20for%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-notetaker-work-meetings-tech-save-time-boost-efficiency-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20bullet-point%20summaries%20of%20a%20larger%20piece%20of%20text%20or%20audio.%3C%2Fa%3E%20You%20can%20imagine%20how%20great%20this%20is%20for%20college%20students%2C%20or%20for%20people%20who%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20meetings%20and%20sales%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20this%20really%20still%20doesn't%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20appeal%20to%20me.%20As%20a%20journalist%2C%20recording%20and%20transcribing%20conversations%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20job%2C%20and%20something%20that%20