0Chesky%3C%2Fa%3E%20founded%20Airbnb%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV6h_EDcj12k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20his%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20was%20an%20entrepreneur.%20His%20mom's%20response%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20you're%20unemployed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dagobert%20Renouf%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f92d6e1a9cbb014deac2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDagobert%20Renouf%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisconnect%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20founders%20and%20non-founders%20at%20the%20table.%3Cp%3EDagobert%20Renouf%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Chris%20Pisarski's%20family%2C%20the%20rub%20was%20that%20he%20had%20to%20take%20calls%20on%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPisarski's%20startup%2C%20Crustdata%2C%20has%20a%20dev%20team%20based%20in%20Vietnam.%20There's%20no%20Thanksgiving%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20Pisarski%20said%2C%20so%20he%20needed%20to%20take%20calls.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20doing%20this%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20remembered%20his%20family%20saying.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20making%20any%20money%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20help%20that%20Pisarski%20recently%20moved%20from%20a%20top-floor%20Chelsea%20apartment%20to%20a%20basement%2C%20or%20that%20he%20had%20to%20raise%20his%20voice%20on%20the%20call%20during%20a%20%26quot%3Brelaxing%26quot%3B%20holiday%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20also%20had%20to%20skip%20out%20on%20the%20family%20tradition%20of%20mall%20shopping%20and%20movie-watching%20on%20Black%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20concern%2C%20but%20mostly%20confusion%2C%26quot%3B%20Pisarski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242ec58a2-3ba6-430c-bba5-f28a0bcc51aa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20families%20who%20get%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20is%20so%20perplexed%20by%20the%20work%20of%20being%20a%20startup%20founder.%20But%20the%20clued-in%20family%20can%20prove%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20challenge%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20they%20may%20start%20asking%20hard-hitting%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBond%20founder%20Chloe%20Samaha's%20parents%20are%20both%20entrepreneurs.%20Thanksgiving%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20talk%20and%20grilling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dad's%20favorite%20question%20is%3A%20How%20many%20customers%20did%20you%20close%20today%3F%26quot%3B%20Samaha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20table%20are%20Samaha's%20aunts%20and%20uncles%2C%20who%20she%20says%20are%20critical%20of%20AI%20and%20believe%20the%20tech%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hiring-white-collar-recession-jobs-tech-new-data-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20people's%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(Bond%2C%20Samaha's%20company%2C%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20chief%20of%20staff.%26quot%3B)%20The%20San%20Francisco-based%20founder%20uses%20the%20example%20of%20the%20calculator%20with%20these%20family%20members%3B%20students%20continued%20to%20learn%20math%20even%20after%20its%20advent%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chloe%20Samaha%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6920765f89026fbb4d0e23b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChloe%20Samaha%20said%20Thanksgiving%20was%20for%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20talk%20and%20grilling.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EChloe%20Samaha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKarun%20Kaushik%20remembers%20when%20people%20doubted%20him.%20In%20those%20pre-revenue%20days%2C%20with%20less%20funding%20to%20point%20to%2C%20Kaushik%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20justify%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20clearly%20serious%20now%3